text: Nicola Regitano (died 1533) was a Roman Catholic prelate who served as Bishop of Nicastro (1533). (in Latin) ==Biography== On 3 Mar 1533, Nicola Regitano was appointed during the papacy of Pope Clement VII as Bishop of Nicastro."Bishop Nicola Regitano" Catholic-Hierarchy.org. David M. Cheney. Retrieved March 21, 2016 He served as Bishop of Nicastro until his death in Sep 1533. == References == ==External links and additional sources== * (for Chronology of Bishops) * (for Chronology of Bishops) Category:16th-century Roman Catholic bishops Category:Bishops appointed by Pope Clement VII Category:1533 deaths
